Simple Network Tanks (uses SDL 1.2)


===============================================
Compiling:
make

===============================================
Starting:
./sntanks [port] [hostname]

	port: server port
	hostname: server hostname

if no hostname given -> game will start as server on given port
if no port and hostname given -> game will start as server on standart port 7777
